index.html.description:
This is an online mirror of my collection of art, skewing towards comics, games, animation and character design. Like a personal Pinterest, it is intended to be powered by hotlinks and lightweight in terms of storage.
Head on over to the Artist_List! ...I don't think I can have a DataView query in the index yet.
